	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">金属和珍珠搭配的首饰很美，没有耳洞也可以</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-30 07:01:54 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">4</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">89</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
<!-- 传入参数：article -->

<a href="/articles/24702.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/24702/indexMediumPc2/24702.jpg?1459314855" alt="为了体现蜂蜜的不同特点，她做了两种性格的包装">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/17/medium/17.png?1411569501" alt="设计">
			<span>设计</span>
		</p>
